{"tid":1407263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(加油系列) 全港最大慈善機構都為『8.5罷工』出聲","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:19:01.000Z","uid":167451,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96d072da0c6dc715937a48ed83eec53ed022ba54","tid":1407263,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:04:54.000Z","msg":"【8.5罷工】馬會CEO應家柏致函員工：尊重同事參與罷工決定<br />\n反對《逃犯條例》風波持續，繼多次遊行示威活動後，有網民發起周一（5日）全港三罷活動，通過罷工、罷市、罷課迫使政府回應五大訴求。香港賽馬會行政總裁應家柏今日（4日）向員工發信，表示尊重馬會同事想以罷工方式表達訴求的決定。<br />\n指馬會尊重言論自由<br />\n應家柏在信中表示，賽馬會尊重言論自由，願意傾聽，並可以接納不同聲音，因而尊重有同事希望通過參加罷工的方式表達意見。他亦表示，員工亦要尊重選擇明天返回機構工作的其他同事。<br />\n關心近來香港局勢發展<br />\n應家柏表示，自己非常關心近來香港的局勢發展，認為社會分化對相關長遠利益有害。他認為，自己是馬會的行政總裁，亦是馬會其他僱員的同事，希望無論時局如何，大家需要保持團結，同時亦要尊重同事有不同意見。<br />\n他強調，馬會並不是以商業利益為目的，而是希望令社會更好。<br />\n應家柏並表明，互相的信任及尊重，不僅有利於個分支、部門及個人在公司運作時合作，也是開啟對話、尋找解決之道的重要基礎。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE:<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/360061/8-5罷工-馬會ceo應家柏致函員工-尊重同事參與罷工決定?utm_campaign=yahooexchange2018&amp;utm_source=relatedlink&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F360061%2F8-5%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5-%E9%A6%AC%E6%9C%83ceo%E6%87%89%E5%AE%B6%E6%9F%8F%E8%87%B4%E5%87%BD%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5-%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%3Futm_campaign%3Dyahooexchange2018%26utm_source%3Drelatedlink%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&d=wovbC19maxltJNBkbBY4lC%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=fd133438\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/360061/8-5罷工-馬會ceo應家柏致函員工-尊重同事參與罷工決定?utm_campaign=yahooexchange2018&amp;utm_source=relatedlink&amp;utm_medium=referral</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家加油!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"57e17f847813c32d47b7960371bab88f069d16a8","tid":1407263,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n8月5日全港被罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1405650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1405650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"39dc879158da44bb2b8d02abe2b2afdb8072ace5","tid":1407263,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:05:36.000Z","msg":"DOG CLUB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6490bf2bb5c627111f1193042d96d517a665c527","tid":1407263,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"好多機構都開始反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adad71542aafe695aa00c424c5ef75c6c2a645f","tid":1407263,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:10:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2692208a967d52c3038d50bac8f4708aa95135ee","tid":1407263,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"好滾動"},{"pid":"3f5b115ec11cf4b965ef67ced3cac7832ef167e4","tid":1407263,"uid":298349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:19:01.000Z","msg":"我無野講"}]}